---
import Check from "../assets/svg/check.svg";
import Shield from "../assets/svg/shape-file-01.svg";
import File from "../assets/svg/shape-file-02.svg";
import Plus from "../assets/svg/plus.svg";
---
<section id="solutions" class="py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <header class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-primary font-semibold">Nos solutions</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mt-2">Un accompagnement complet</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base-content/70">
        De l'audit à la maintenance, nous déployons des solutions adaptées aux exigences des professionnels de santé.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <img src={Shield.src} alt="Sécurité" class="h-10 w-10" />
          <h3 class="card-title">Sécurité & conformité</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><img src={Check.src} alt="" class="h-5 w-5"/> Sauvegardes et chiffrement</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><img src={Check.src} alt="" class="h-5 w-5"/> RGPD, HDS, bonnes pratiques</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <img src={File.src} alt="Logiciels" class="h-10 w-10" />
          <h3 class="card-title">Logiciels & intégrations</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><img src={Check.src} alt="" class="h-5 w-5"/> Dossiers patients et téléservices</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><img src={Check.src} alt="" class="h-5 w-5"/> Matériel & réseaux compatibles</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <img src={Plus.src} alt="Support" class="h-10 w-10" />
          <h3 class="card-title">Support & maintenance</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><img src={Check.src} alt="" class="h-5 w-5"/> Intervention sur site / à distance</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><img src={Check.src} alt="" class="h-5 w-5"/> Supervision proactive</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
